{"tid":962271,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣佈蘇蛇係我獌真命天子","createTime":"2018-12-30T17:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T11:34:10.000Z","uid":117762,"like":9,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"682173e6433dd1d2728468ed887bf3b5f7fc04fd","tid":962271,"uid":117762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T17:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2fnmKiJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2fnmKiJ.gif&h=ac26c1ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>講真 <br />\n我唔知以前既So Sir帶波係點 <br />\n只係知佢有性格都有成績 <br />\n再睇佢既YOUTUBE教練片 <br />\n純粹講個種PASSION <br />\n直情係HYPER版既費SIR <br />\n<br />\n大家都知曼聯更衣室要變 <br />\n要建立新既秩序 <br />\n大家同時又好驚So Sir教細球會既經驗會摧毀晒曼聯所有既傳統 <br />\n個種矛盾搞到大家都好想So Sir快手幫手換代引援同時又好想有人快D接佢走 <br />\n<br />\n但由賽後訪問黎睇 <br />\n我係度諗 20年前佢就係費SIR指定既後備殺手 <br />\n20年過去 阿SIR終於離開曼聯 So Sir 歷盡鉛華 人生不在初相逢 <br />\n一個大勝不驕 步步為營 同時足球智慧熱情還在頂峰既So Sir<br />\n會唔會就係個個我地心目中既阿SIR </strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/39zcQYK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F39zcQYK.gif&h=90acee74&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b866e81351483411a299c716012f1f2724f0d9a5","tid":962271,"uid":32486,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T17:33:02.000Z","msg":"等睇 so sir 比人炒個陣<br />\n呢個 post 變 環保 post"},{"pid":"3253f160a4f7b6b51c415d952e194c20d01e6f5d","tid":962271,"uid":25086,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T19:53:55.000Z","msg":"個po令人諗起當初敢帥同摩狗上任個時獌狗打到成地都係咁陣腥味<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea8ac8ed36c129bb02b4a78c36641feb4a8432e","tid":962271,"uid":74278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T20:08:37.000Z","msg":"明明上年完季獌都有81分<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236efa625c3c9f4d3447f66dde26bfe64aae20b4","tid":962271,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T21:26:41.000Z","ms